[2mFind the century anchor. Starting with year [34mY[39m:
 - take the century digits [3mC = Y / 100[23m
 - in a four century cycle its index is [3mF = C % 4[23m
 - the resulting increment is [3mI = F * 5[23m
 - add Tuesday and get [3mA = [33mTuesday + I[39m[23m

Find the year anchor. Starting with year [34mY[39m:
 - note the century anchor [3mA[23m
 - take the last two digits [3mT = Y % 100[23m
 - divide them by twelve [3mD = T / 12[23m
 - and take the reminder [3mR = T % 12[23m
 - the resulting increment is [3mI = (D + R) + R/4[23m
 - add the century anchor to get [3mW = [33mA + I[39m[23m

Find the weekday. Starting with date [34mD[39m:
 - note the year anchor [3mW[23m
 - this months doomsday is [3mO[23m
 - the resulting increment is [3mI = D - O[23m
 - add the year anchor to get [3mR = [33mW + I[39m[23m
